Group Project: Legal Judgment Prediction using Deep Learning Techniques

Machine Learning [CS3244]

Author (alphabetical order): Chen Guoyi; Leng Jin De, Joel; Michael Hui; Wang Silang; Zeng Bethany.
Supervisors: Prof. Bresson Xavier, Dr. Lin Xiaoqiang

Training Dataset with Labeled Features


The datasets we utilized are publicly available and were obtained from an open-source government website. Our group's Python code assigned the featured labels. These datasets and labels are intended solely for training AI models and should not be used for purposes other than academic research.

The dataset is available for download on the specified website; please click the hyperlink to access and download it.
